Package: ReMIXTURE
Title: ReMIXTURE
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("M Timothy", "Rabanus-Wallace", , "mtrw85@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: 
    Implementation of the ReMIXTURE method to quantify how (genetic or other) diversity is distributed and shared between groups, and to create pretty and intuitive plots showing this on a globe. An earlier version of this method is described in Rabanus-Wallace & Tripodi et al. (2021), this newer version differs significantly.
